00:34:05,520 --> 00:34:06,800
Shi berada di mana?

497
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,080
Di Biro Ziyi,

498
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:09,480
Yu Niang mengawasinya.

499
00:34:12,440 --> 00:34:13,360
Logikanya,

500
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:15,760
seharusnya di sisi Kepala Dayang Cheng
tak ada lagi orang yang bisa dia gunakan.

501
00:34:16,360 --> 00:34:17,080
Lagi pula,

502
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:19,120
bisa-bisanya menyelamatkannya

503
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:21,400
dari Kamp Jiangqi
tanpa sepengetahuan siapa pun.

504
00:34:21,630 --> 00:34:22,840
Pelakunya orang Qiu Ziliang.

505
00:34:25,630 --> 00:34:26,960
Dia dan Cheng Xi tidak tinggal lama

506
00:34:27,080 --> 00:34:28,440
dan menyadari pengintaian kami,

507
00:34:28,560 --> 00:34:29,600
jadi kabur.

508
00:34:30,150 --> 00:34:31,560
Kaki kanan orang ini terluka.

509
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:35,230
Dia Benteng Kiri.

510
00:34:46,710 --> 00:34:47,480
Jadi,

511
00:34:47,710 --> 00:34:49,710
Cheng Ruoyu memang adalah Wang Ruoling,

512
00:34:49,960 --> 00:34:50,670
benar, 'kan?

513
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:05,040
Sudah kuduga,

514
00:35:05,440 --> 00:35:06,800
dengan sifat Qiu Ziliang,
mana mungkin dia

515
00:35:06,920 --> 00:35:08,240
melakukan pengobatan tertutup
selama empat bulan?

516
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:10,040
Ternyata dia beralih
dari terang menjadi gelap,

517
00:35:10,400 --> 00:35:11,920
menunggu sampai
kita kalang kabut sendiri.

518
00:35:18,240 --> 00:35:19,440
Ling Ling?

519
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:22,880
Ling Ling datang.

520
00:35:24,600 --> 00:35:25,360
Baginda sudah bilang,

521
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:27,600
sekarang Nona Cheng Ruoyu yang
paling berada dalam bahaya.

522
00:35:27,960 --> 00:35:28,720
Qiu Ziliang

523
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,800
kemungkinan besar
sudah mengetahui identitasnya.

524
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:32,840
Xiu.

525
00:35:33,040 --> 00:35:33,800
Kalian pergi dulu.

526
00:35:33,960 --> 00:35:34,360
Baik.

527
00:35:34,680 --> 00:35:35,360
Ikut denganku.

528
00:36:00,040 --> 00:36:00,840
Kau sudah datang.

529
