594
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:36,880
Baginda.

595
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:39,760
Hamba mana berani
punya harapan seperti itu.

596
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,120
Huaizhi.

597
00:41:44,960 --> 00:41:45,680
Hamba di sini.

598
00:41:50,000 --> 00:41:50,600
Tidak ada apa-apa.

599
00:41:54,840 --> 00:41:55,440
(Huaizhi.)

600
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,520
(Semoga suatu hari)

601
00:41:58,480 --> 00:41:59,680
(bisa seperti yang kau harapkan.)

602
00:42:03,080 --> 00:42:04,280
Kau bantulah aku atur,

603
00:42:04,760 --> 00:42:06,040
aku ingin bertemu Paman Guang.

604
00:42:08,560 --> 00:42:09,240
Baik.

605
00:42:19,820 --> 00:42:22,500
