608
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:34,420
(Demikian.)

609
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,080
Bagaimana?

610
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:38,800
Luka luarnya tidak parah,

611
00:42:39,520 --> 00:42:42,680
tapi otaknya sepertinya terguncang.

612
00:42:43,720 --> 00:42:46,480
Mungkin bisa mengingat
hal-hal waktu kecil.

613
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:47,600
Maksudmu,

614
00:42:48,520 --> 00:42:49,760
