631
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:52,160
Selalu seperti ini.

632
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:55,320
Momennya tidak tepat.

633
00:43:58,840 --> 00:43:59,680
Dulu,

634
00:44:00,880 --> 00:44:02,240
tidak berani mengakui.

635
00:44:03,600 --> 00:44:04,440
Sekarang,

636
00:44:07,880 --> 00:44:08,800
